class Solution {
public:
    bool isMatch(const char *s, const char *p) {
        // Start typing your C/C++ solution below
        // DO NOT write int main() function
        
        
        bool allStar = true;
        int m = 0;
        int n = 0;
        
        while(s[m] != 0){
            m++;
        }
        while(p[n] != 0){
            if(p[n] != '*'){
                allStar = false;
            }
            n++;
        }
  
        if(n == 0){
            return m == 0;
        }else if (m == 0){
            return allStar;
        }
        

        bool table[m+1][n+1];
        
        table[m][n] = true;
        for(int i = 0; i < m; i++){
            table[i][n] = false;
        }
        for(int j = n-1; j >= 0 ; j--){
            if(p[j] == '*'){
                table[m][j] = table[m][j+1];
            }else{
                table[m][j] = false;   
            }
        }
        
        
        
        
        //for(int i = 0; i < m+1; i++){
        //    for(int j = 0; j < n+1; j++){
        //        table[i][j] = false;
        //    }
        //}

        //    table[m][j] = (p[j] == '*');
        //}
        
        
        //if(p[n-1] == '*' || p[n-1] == '?' || p[n-1] == s[m-1]){
        //    table[m-1][n-1] = true;
        //}
        
        
        for(int i = m-1; i >= 0; i--){
            for(int j = n-1; j >= 0; j--){
                
                if(p[j] == '*'){
                    table[i][j] = table[i+1][j] || table[i][j+1];  
                }
                else if(p[j] == '?'){
                    table[i][j] = table[i+1][j+1];
                }
                else{
                    table[i][j] = (p[j] == s[i]) && table[i+1][j+1];
                }
            }
        }
        return table[0][0];
        
        return false;

        }else if( *p == *s || (*p == '?' && *s != 0)){
